{"tid":81361,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"好撚羨慕有天份嘅人呀","createTime":"2017-01-15T09:19:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T11:42:50.000Z","uid":38215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f0284cce97609e1009007304ff9d8d31ceaf428","tid":81361,"uid":38215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T09:19:47.000Z","msg":"中學開始學結他識咗掃chord好多年<br />\n近年先開始聽Jimi Hendrix SRV 呢d<br />\n開始咗認真學下點彈結他<br />\n但係好多時候花好多好多時間進步到好少<br />\n偏偏身邊有d人聽幾聽就明點彈<br />\n<br />\n唔止音樂<br />\n踢波掟鏢設計冇天份嘅我跟本點都做 / 諗唔到有天份嘅人嘅野<br />\n真係好羨慕有天份嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e29b7342fac98a593a4fc48a9feb61f94ecbc4f","tid":81361,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T09:20:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6972d2ea1570b0841f6a70f315b21c5ac19f22a0","tid":81361,"uid":38215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T09:21:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你柒頭</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPPFuhKrZwmSMamoooyQDzBNU2bjMQYeuAozsyBJTESXJ?filename=2v1j8c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2v1j8c9.jpg&h=bca814b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83549e868f933783d28e3ae98077b86562cf6e53","tid":81361,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T09:24:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97c22af7f07af91cc7eec5de1cdcc4e2b9be333b","tid":81361,"uid":31998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T09:26:53.000Z","msg":"學結他果度，我覺得係學習方法同埋練習質素會比較影響到個進度<br />\n當然我都遇過天份好高，但天份唔高既人用岩方法去學/練唔會太慢<br />\n<br />\n利申：全職教結他 N 年"},{"pid":"5b3e6eb0381984e89f43533829f0e45d2246163a","tid":81361,"uid":12152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T09:28:40.000Z","msg":"世界就係咁唔公平<br />\n面對現實吧"},{"pid":"22264c8c2e9b3062a52a1b6c532b9c3d093b9dc6","tid":81361,"uid":38215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T09:31:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學結他果度，我覺得係學習方法同埋練習質素會比較影響到個進度<br />\n當然我都遇過天份好高，但天份唔高既人用岩方法去學/練唔會太慢<br />\n<br />\n利申：全職教結他 N 年</blockquote><br />\n全職教野搵唔搵到食?<br />\n係咪要捱好耐?"},{"pid":"969c3581e7adcfd0d853cc9481b3c9050cdf6afe","tid":81361,"uid":31998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:42:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>學結他果度，我覺得係學習方法同埋練習質素會比較影響到個進度<br />\n當然我都遇過天份好高，但天份唔高既人用岩方法去學/練唔會太慢<br />\n<br />\n利申：全職教結他 N 年</blockquote><br />\n全職教野搵唔搵到食?<br />\n係咪要捱好耐?</blockquote><br />\n仲捱緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我應該係 freelance musician，唔係淨教結他 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係淨教結他都幾難搵，因為結他唔係果D 有家長迫考級既樂器（古典結他除外）<br />\n我同時會出埋婚禮 gig、打譜、orchestration<br />\n收入唔算好好，我其實考慮緊不再全職"}]}